                            <p style="font-family: 'Times New Roman', serif;">Both of my grandmas loved to sew and do other crafts. They both made many different things that they would share with friends and family. They both taught me different skills that I applied to my own creative skills. When one of them passed, I decided to make memory baby quilts for myself and my siblings to honor her. As I made them, I reflected on the things I had learned from both her and my other grandma. Hence the name- A Little Bit of Grandma.</p>
